overview: Biggs Peabody gets what he wants, Joan Reyes fights for her son's life, Tyrannosaurus Kincaid meets the locals. It's a long road out of hell, but it's a longer road out of Cuddy County.
tagline: It's a long road out of Hell, but it's a longer road out of Cuddy County.
title: Tyrannosaurus Kincaid
